{"tid":1340981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要光復元朗嘅兄弟入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:42:16.000Z","uid":45071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca05e7fd655ab40226f91d1140c8d8d866ca3c4","tid":1340981,"uid":45071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"我完全明白，今晚元朗呢單野係令人好撚嬲！我都好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但明顯地呢單野係政府同一部分嘅牛屎閪聯手搞出黎<br />\n<br />\n其實呢班牛屎佬，港英政府已經睇佢地唔順眼，大陸佬就更加係，如果唔係都唔使推個明日大嶼出黎，搞到佢地啲地一文不值<br />\n<br />\n而今日，港共政權借呢一部分牛屎佬，辣慶香港人，要我地入去同佢地硬碰<br />\n<br />\n結果有三：<br />\n一，我地贏，贏哂，拆哂祠堂起哂墳頭，幫港共政府移除一坐大山<br />\n<br />\n二，一半一半，克驚可以走出黎調停，扮哂野，博挽回民心<br />\n<br />\n三，我地輸，港共政府借牛屎佬隻手打傷我地嘅人，打擊我地士氣<br />\n<br />\n三個結果港共政府都有得益<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"77cbfd32ddd815ae12f8dbdad9968c53ccd92c85","tid":1340981,"uid":45071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"廢文自推"},{"pid":"aaf8fcf222744d8eccb09ec39e946264854b9b37","tid":1340981,"uid":45071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f09647f64f7732ed2c8f92823eab4044b8798f7","tid":1340981,"uid":45071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"啱唔啱用都可以討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.